            "introduction": {
              "introduction": "　As the vanguard of HRT Berry, Bomi humiliates her enemies with her taunting illusions.\n\n　Until a few years ago, Bomi used to be a member of a girl group produced by a large entertainment company. But she was asked to leave when doubts were raised on the group's exploitation, because Bomi kept falling asleep whenever she was not dancing.\n　She wants to show off her new dance moves she made in her dreams, but ever since Miya streamed Bomi talking in her sleep, her sleep streams are more popular than her dance streams. According to the NetTube statistics, 83% of the donations received by HRT Berry comes from Bomi's sleep streams. "
